        {
            "title": "中國貨船安全通過霍爾木茲海峽 伊朗：僅針對美以歐",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/19IWEjvhqkUzCdJf6nf1Mg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/cnyes_hk_559/50d83820898e19ddc74bb1ec5fee434a\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在美以襲擊伊朗之際，全世界船隻大多遠遠望著霍爾木茲海峽，不敢輕易靠近。印度新德里電視台（NDTV）周三（4 日）爆料，稱為感謝中國在衝突中的立場，伊朗表示僅允許中國船隻通海峽。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據《彭博》報導，周四凌晨一艘散貨船為安全通過海峽，船舶識別訊號中的目的地是「中國所有」（CHINA OWNER）。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗伊斯蘭革命衛隊周四說，在荷姆茲海峽僅對美國、以色列、歐洲及其西方盟友船隻關閉。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">航運數據公司 Kpler 的船舶追蹤數據顯示，這艘名為「鐵娘子號」（Iron Maiden）的散貨船周四凌晨將船舶識別訊號從「待命」（For Orders）改為「中國所有」（CHINA OWNER），同時沿阿曼海岸線突破航道。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c62aeff6-84c4-344a-a8a1-9cdcfbf4d97a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「鐵娘子號」自去年 12 月以來一直在波斯灣活動，執行了多批貨物運輸任務。營運該船的興達航運（上海）有限公司發言人表示，不會就具體航運操作發表評論，尤其是在相關消息可能影響船員安全的情況下。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這艘船的登記船東 Mi-Das Line SA 也沒有公布聯繫方式，註冊地址與日本航運公司洞雲汽船有關聯。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一舉動發生在霍爾木茲海峽安全形勢急劇惡化之際。自美國和以色列對伊朗展開空襲以來，這一全球最重要的能源運輸咽喉幾乎陷入停滯。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">更多鉅亨報導</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%B2%A8%E8%88%B9%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E%E8%8D%B7%E5%A7%86%E8%8C%B2%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD-%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97-%E5%83%85%E9%87%9D%E5%B0%8D%E7%BE%8E%E4%BB%A5%E6%AD%90-200002533.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-06 07:15:56",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美股日誌｜ 油不是80年代 油價升至24年以來新高",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美股日誌｜ 油不是80年代 油價升至24年以來新高\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/EmQCsZfaNoWyVkxE3pBSNg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/b9d50650-18e1-11f1-bfef-b60337aaa5bd\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美股日誌｜ 油不是80年代 油價升至24年以來新高</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國股市周四收市下跌，華爾街未能延續前一交易日的反彈走勢。中東衝突持續成為市場焦點，同時油價再度急升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">道指盤中一度大跌1100點，收市下跌約1.6%，即逾780點；標普500指數下跌約0.6%；科技權重較高的納斯達克綜合指數跌幅較小，下跌 0.3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">市場仍聚焦中東局勢。美國與以色列聯盟與伊朗之間的攻擊已蔓延至區內多地。周四為衝突爆發第六日，暫未見緩和跡象。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伊朗為石油輸出國組織第四大產油國，其產能受損對大宗商品及股市均帶來廣泛影響，市場憂慮油價急升，或迫使聯儲局在波動的市場環境下重新評估利率政策。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-b7d9a1de-0752-4ae2-b7e9-d9f75e0dc5ce-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價再次上揚，布蘭特原油期貨觸2024 年以來最高水平，預料將進一步推高汽油價格。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://mobile.yahoo.com/finance?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_article_&amp;af_sub1=Acquisition&amp;af_sub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_&amp;uuid=eDFkEhESdIhPGYRE2850\"><ins>下載Yahoo財經APP</ins></a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3月5日（星期四）市况</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:道瓊斯指數;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EDJI\"> <ins>道瓊斯指數</ins></a> 跌784.67點或1.61%，報47,954.74點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:標普500指數;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EGSPC\"> <ins>標普500指數</ins></a> 跌38.79點或0.56%，報6,830.71點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:納斯達克指數;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EIXIC\"> <ins>納斯達克指數</ins></a> 跌58.5點或0.26%，報22,748.99點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期油;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CL=F\"> <ins>紐約4月期油</ins></a> 收報78.87元一桶，升4.21美元或5.64%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期金;cpos:6;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/GC=F\"> <ins>紐約4月期金</ins></a> 收報5,093.3美元一盎司，跌41.4美元或0.81%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:比特幣;cpos:7;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BTC-USD/\"> <ins>比特幣</ins></a> 截至美東時間下午4時報71,248.12美元，跌1,862.51美元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:8;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:美國10年期國債息率;cpos:8;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5ETNX\"> <ins>美國10年期國債息率</ins></a> 收報4.146厘。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國2月28日初次申領失業救濟人數為21.3萬，與上期持平。預期為21.5萬。市場關注周五公布的每月就業報告，該數據將為投資者提供勞動市場健康狀況的最新線索。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">道指大跌，傳統股受壓，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:9;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:波音;cpos:9;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BA/\">波音</a>(BA.US)跌2.3%、<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:10;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Caterpillar;cpos:10;pos:1;e