        {
            "title": "川普解職國土安全部長諾姆 為第二任期首次更換內閣成員",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">【彭博】— <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:特朗普;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/特朗普\">特朗普</a>解除克里斯蒂·諾姆的國土安全部部長職務，並宣布取代她的是<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:奧克拉荷馬州;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/奧克拉荷馬州\">奧克拉荷馬州</a>聯邦參議員Markwayne Mullin。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特朗普周四在社交媒體上發文稱，這一調整將於3月31日生效。他表示，諾姆將轉任西半球事務特使。這是特朗普第二任期內首次更換內閣成員。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我很高興宣布，來自偉大奧克拉荷馬州、備受尊敬的美國參議員Markwayne Mullin將出任美國國土安全部長，」特朗普寫道，「感謝克里斯蒂在‘國土安全’的服務。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-de3c4773-8802-332e-a90d-edaf5bb95b67-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"克里斯蒂·諾姆Source: Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FcYWFo0msrqza9c6ZgjHXw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/25905452459106f8a4a400f1c3314d47\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">克里斯蒂·諾姆Source: Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">諾姆的永久繼任者需經參議院確認。白宮發言人未說明Mullin是將被正式提名，還是會以代理身份履職。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Mullin表示，他是在特朗普於社交媒體發布該消息前不久接到了總統的電話。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「諾姆承擔了一項非常艱巨的任務，我認為她已在既定情況下盡力而為，」Mullin對記者表示。「我們有機會在既有成果基礎上繼續推進，也有機會改進那些可能未完全按計畫推進的工作。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Trump Leaning Toward Removing Noem as Homeland Security Chief</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">—聯合報導 Kate Sullivan、Angelica Franganillo Diaz.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E8%A7%A3%E8%81%B7%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%9F%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E8%AB%BE%E5%A7%86-%E7%82%BA%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%8C%E4%BB%BB%E6%9C%9F%E9%A6%96%E6%AC%A1%E6%9B%B4%E6%8F%9B%E5%85%A7%E9%96%A3%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1-202055378.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-06 07:15:58",
